text: Nocardioides hankookensis is a Gram-positive, rod-shaped and non-motile bacterium from the genus of Nocardioides which has been isolated from soil from Dokdo in Korea. == References == == Further reading == * ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides hankookensis at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase hankookensis Category:Bacteria described in 2008
title: Nocardioides hankookensis
